{"type": "article", "id": 52105, "title": "史上最简洁Vespa小摩托，挺好看｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-12T23:15:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}, {"id": 28548, "name": "The School of Life"}, {"id": 49259, "name": "OMA建筑事务所"}, {"id": 39252, "name": "GAN"}, {"id": 49260, "name": "Lee Wen De"}, {"id": 49261, "name": "Bright Potato"}, {"id": 49262, "name": "Giulio Iacchetti"}, {"id": 49263, "name": "Ippolito Pestellini Laparelli"}, {"id": 28432, "name": "Neri&Hu"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 297, "image": "img/article/article_show/201804130715310eDmCwtH79zkZbI6.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #0b0080; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #0b0080} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LAN Collection by Neri&amp;Hu for GAN</h3><p>西班牙地毯品牌 GAN，最近请来上海设计工作室 Neri&amp;Hu，为其设计了包括沙发、地毯以及屏风在内的 LAN 系列。整个系列试图挑战我们对现有沙发区配置的刻板印象。</p><p>LAN 这个名字来源于中文“蓝”，代表着这个系列的主色调靛蓝色。从沙发、地毯到屏风，不同类型的网格元素重复跳跃出现。屏风既可以用作分隔空间，也可以置于沙发背后作为装饰背景元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185223AvaWp0FSdzKILGYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.533594\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185223CqrSGtxz7gpd2TEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185223PFj9nx0eCkXRTZhp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185223evRi0TNf2EWqlPX4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185225bcB05CNmOl3uSvKd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.417187\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185232GRIy8cSuxVED9ZBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185231EXN96OxMTnaYqtSh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/gan-partners-with-nerihu-on-a-new-sofa-typology/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>XY180 Collection by Ippolito Pestellini Laparelli</h3><p>受比利时品牌 Delta Light 之邀，荷兰建筑事务所 OMA 合伙人 Ippolito Pestellini Laparelli，结合杆射灯创造了一组线性照明系统 XY 180，围绕着一个铰链夹具，将不同的元素连接在一起，可以形成多种几何图案。</p><p>可调节灯管的功能是环境照明，两种不同类型的聚光灯则主要形成更多的定向光束。每个元素都是单独的组成部分，但每个元素之间又都是相互关联的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0628ijgnj8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185340OxbiGQPdMoH73ShC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185343GOR9BkbJsvma7rpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121853494mfUW2TtdXk7iCS3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185351fDQks4NdeuO8h6wt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185351XMUAEmgklu25q9dB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Vespampère by Giulio Iacchetti</h3><p>Vespa 是意大利摩托车制造商<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%AF%94%E9%9B%85%E4%B9%85\" rel=\"nofollow\">比亚乔</a>旗下的一个子品牌，其产品为两轮轻便踏板式摩托车。自其 1946 年诞生以来一直延续着最初型号的外观，并保持着小巧、紧凑的特点。</p><p>最近，意大利设计师 Giulio Iacchetti 基于其经典轮廓，更新设计了 Vespampère 摩托车，试图在城市交通系统中发挥其更高的灵活性。</p><p>他希望将这款车型变得轻便，删掉了所有多余的东西，所有的控制器、计时器、电量表和指示灯都可以通过应用程序使用无线连接进行访问，仅在仪表盘上创建了一个用于存储智能手机的特殊隔间。从侧面看起来，Vespampère 还是保留了其典型外观，但更简约轻便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121854418jih3wnOds2PJEgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754902\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185443noJ8V9P4cGYe326S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.717073\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185443NoieyA6JacBQY9W3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750306\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185446mqi7HBS9o0ys4NXU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735547\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185450caGRk2Cd4mn9vHAg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745410\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ArNO Wireframe Chair by Bright Potato</h3><p>在今年米兰家具展的卫星展上，设计师 Bright Potato 将推出一款名为 ArNO 的椅子，线条大胆利落，试图引导用户联想到夏日的微风。</p><p>Bright Potato 的线框设计引用了氩气、氮气和氧气这三种组成地球大气的元素，几何形态抓人眼球。ArNO 可叠放，重量轻，耐用，可在室内和户外使用，适用于任何用户选择的环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121855225TPlkNVYHLBi6OJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185522O3yuGr1ev4ERMd05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185523BmaKnRW9GbLQsyfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121855227HJPYFVzLK0IWgCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121855236VY4U7uQNer2cKRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.512000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185523r0mfkxsaiI1zE36o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.551000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/bright-potatos-arno-wireframe-chair-features-expressive-lines/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Phone Detox by The School of Life</h3><p>一项调查表明，我们每天平均要查看手机 85 次，但在伦敦教育组织 The School of Life 看来，这种重度依赖手机的行为已经让我们的生活失衡了。为此，他们推出了一款名为 Phone Detox 的口袋书籍，基本等同于手机大小，内容涵盖了宗教、诗歌、自然、乌托邦甚至死亡等相关话题。</p><p>它的目的是让我们退后一步，沉淀下来多一些思考，而不是简单地消费互联网不断向你投掷的内容。这本书的制作者说，“这就是一个令人愉快的小玩意儿，放下手机屏幕，享受一些停顿下来的时刻。”售价 8 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.theschooloflife.com/shop/phone-detox/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185618OSC9ZJPaUyvIp8fA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185618wGLMx4JfQ8SXRFAY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185618faOTIHmkP2MjU6qo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185618DmLaRMwGNvgqlHVP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185619QKsET4luxpYjzdt8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804121856196KzBaEqlIixD9Utf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185620iVaGCsn2uIgtKkO5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wonder Chair by Lee Wen De</h3><p>近几年，人们越来越清晰地意识到，设计决策对于环境造成的影响，对于那些使用寿命较长的家具开始又了更多期待。设计师 Lee Wen De 的这款 Wonder 座椅试图提出一种解决方案，它考虑到用户不断变化的需求以扩展其可用性。</p><p>Wonder 座椅的多功能性很好实现，只需要翻转它即可。它既可以用作孩子的儿童椅或儿童书桌进行绘画或写作，也可以成为任何青少年或成人的全尺寸椅子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185651pgeLcF4s95oq31fK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185651oaO8i9C0sFgZlRrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185652MknfjlWvNQxzsGDC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.763810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185652GbFaexPKMUEdlstn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180412185651I2YBdkflOezFMGm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/04/10/a-lifetime-of-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}